vidhāya antarāyati byavadhānaṃ karotīti kattari appaccayaṃ vidhāya antaro byavadhāyako natthetesanti anantarā. Yathā ‘rukkhā vanante’ttha rukkhā samuditāvekavanabyapadesaṃ labhante, tathātrāpi byañjanā samuditāvete saṃyogabyapadesagocarattaṃ paṭipajjante.
